    N1["1. neo-execution-core: Lifecycle shows how the unit reaches observable runtime operation."]
    N2["2. Configuration: input model, output model, boundary policy"]
    N3["3. Input intake: L2 batch | previous state root | execution parameters"]
    N4["4. Normalization: shape external inputs into a verifiable domain model"]
    N5["5. Execution or verification: Validate batch shape | Apply deterministic transition | Commit new state root"]
    N6["6. Commit or output: execution trace | new state root | public proof inputs"]
    N7["7. Consumption: neo-zkvm-guest | neo-zkvm-host | gateway services"]
    N8["8. Operation: input digest, output digest, state change, and rejection reason"]
    N1 --> N2
    N2 --> N3
    N3 --> N4
    N4 --> N5
    N5 --> N6
    N6 --> N7
    N7 --> N8
